    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-spec 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six engine. This unit boasts individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double-VANOS system that provides a broad, linear powerband. The 6-speed manual transmission offers precise engagement, sending power to the rear wheels through a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system refresh. The chassis retains its legendary handling characteristics thanks to refreshed bushings and a well-sorted multi-link rear suspension. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical synchronization and compression remain excellent, making this a perfect candidate for the purist seeking performance over concours perfection.",
